title/1: Definix on Klaytn Chain G2 launch!
content/1:
Definix Generation 2 service is launched on Klaytn Chain.
We keep trying the best effort to satisfy our holders.
content/2:
If you are a vFINIX holder, you can make your voice to Definix ecosystem. 
Cast vote and become a part of Definix.
content/3:
Definix is always listening to the voices of holders.
If there are any inconveniences or improvements to the beta service, please give us feedback.
